Package: inferclientllmtool
Title: R Client for LLM Tool Inference API and Ollama
Version: 1.3.0
Authors@R:
    person("Antoine", "Lemor", email = "antoine.lemor@umontreal.ca", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: R client SDK for the Transformer Inference API (infer-api-llm-tool).
    Classify texts at scale using models trained with LLM Tool, or generate text
    with decoder LLMs via the server's Ollama integration. All inference runs on
    the remote API server.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
